#

Pan-Seared Duck Breast with Cherry-Balsamic Reduction

$30
750 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-free

Tags:

gourmetspecial occasionmeat lovers

Description

A succulent and flavorful duck breast paired with a sweet-tart cherry-balsamic reduction.

Ingredients

  • duck breast: 2 pieces
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • balsamic vinegar: 1/2 cup
  • chicken stock: 1/2 cup
  • cherry preserves: 1/3 cup
  • fresh thyme: 1 teaspoon, chopped
